          "name": "Goal Alignment Checker",
          "description": "Reviews tasks and initiatives against high-level goals and OKRs to ensure strategic alignment. Analyzes current activities, assesses alignment levels, identifies gaps, and provides actionable recommendations for better goal-oriented focus.",
          "instructions": "Provide your high-level goals or OKRs and list your current activities and tasks. The routine will analyze how well your current work aligns with your strategic objectives and recommend adjustments to improve focus and effectiveness.",
